      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/foreigner-investors-set-to-end-emerging-asia-stock-buying-streak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球资金正在从亚洲新兴市场撤出，连续五个月的股票购买热潮因美国降息预期的减弱而结束。]]></description>
